{"tid":266895,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"Exchange 去旅行 短遊 Split","createTime":"2017-06-01T23:15:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-04T14:57:37.000Z","uid":94033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2b56e8adcf3e450cf5f37035ce07a95e09d6c76a","tid":266895,"uid":94033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T23:15:06.000Z","msg":"第一次係度 post 遊記, 唔鐘意唔好屌得甘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">btw, 知我係邊個切勿相認</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4269/34999899596_b2a4165edb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F5%2F4269%2F34999899596_b2a4165edb.jpg&h=626d2746&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>Split 的海港</em><br />\n<br />\n這是我與女友第一次單獨出遊, 看似意義重大, 但決定目的地過程頗為兒戲, 我們上航空公司網站, 嗯? 去 Split 好便宜! 之後就成行了。<br />\n來到 Split 市中心已經是傍晚時份。我們決定到海邊走走, 順便吃個晚餐。<br />\nOld Town 內的食肆大多都很貴 (100KRN 起跳), 是遊客屠房, 我們這對窮遊的學生情侶吃不起, 但好多店舖已經關門。正當想回 BNB 附近用餐時, 我們發現一間外賣店, 有便宜的 pizza 和餡餅, 還有 8KRN 一球雪糕, 賣相十分討好, 味道比英國的好吃太多了。這些雪糕馬上就俘虜了女友的心 (接下來幾天每天最少吃一杯)。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i1.wp.com/www.mammalovestravel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/20150619_203845.jpg?resize=900%2C506\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fwww.mammalovestravel.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F07%2F20150619_203845.jpg%3Fresize%3D900%252C506&h=a551aa99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>Split 的雪糕 (source: <a href=\"http://www.mammalovestravel.com/top-things-to-do-with-your-kids-in-croatia/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mammalovestravel.com%2Ftop-things-to-do-with-your-kids-in-croatia%2F&d=Lz%2FlKVMzjY173D09amOymb5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=a1c735a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mammalovestravel.com/top-things-to-do-with-your-kids-in-croatia/</a>)</em><br />\n<br />\n我們把食物帶到海邊吃, 我們都憧憬著一個在微風下看海的浪漫晚餐,但一出到海邊,我們一心期待的微風變成刺骨的寒風, 我們速速吃完手上凡食物後就回BNB了。<br />\n<br />\n今日出著咁多先, 聽日再出文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a81561b44c98f586eb98b999800b0cc370a87e7f","tid":266895,"uid":50980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T23:45:49.000Z","msg":"想問下split 玩到兩日嗎?  本來諗住去hvar 但係又好似差不多咁"},{"pid":"0aace26f7266fac2da0f05dda7ae924290ca6d55","tid":266895,"uid":37803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T23:52:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下split 玩到兩日嗎?  本來諗住去hvar 但係又好似差不多咁</blockquote><br />\n藍洞出海一日遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ef271e2a0ee32eb2561dfe0468df81ce6d4bcec","tid":266895,"uid":94033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T00:43:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下split 玩到兩日嗎?  本來諗住去hvar 但係又好似差不多咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我又玩到 wor, 上 Majan Mountains, 去下 Green Market, 再睇 Bell Tower, 舊皇宮地牢, 教堂, 真係玩到兩個 full day, 不過我玩攝影 (我影完就被女朋友捉著影合照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 所以影相耗時係長D"},{"pid":"79f51f6a64f60f8f80db97ca316e637641f864db","tid":266895,"uid":94033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T00:44:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想問下split 玩到兩日嗎?  本來諗住去hvar 但係又好似差不多咁</blockquote><br />\n藍洞出海一日遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都想, 不過成 400幾 500KRN, 好貴, 同埋我係果邊天氣唔太好, 未必去到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc954e9e529b0e363007df610f1094ae2c51274","tid":266895,"uid":50980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T00:52:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想問下split 玩到兩日嗎?  本來諗住去hvar 但係又好似差不多咁</blockquote><br />\n藍洞出海一日遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇台灣人去藍洞屌哂鬼  坐個幾鐘大飛睇十分鐘  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26d00af6ed050442d50df55f9cbaaf58cd905c80","tid":266895,"uid":5181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco