ar 但係又好似差不多咁</blockquote><br />\n藍洞出海一日遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇台灣人去藍洞屌哂鬼  坐個幾鐘大飛睇十分鐘  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲要勁早出發, 分分鍾半邊身未訓醒 (好似 9am 左右就會係 hvar 出發, 即係要搭6am 班船去 Hvar <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)</blockquote><br />\n我之前search過split 都有團出  唔駛特登去hvar 上  同埋佢係會上島俾時間你遊城  都會玩成日   所以我都諗過下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53c3b6a387e017d3f6dfa8d3ba468ce21c3ee728","tid":266895,"uid":94033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T03:25:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問下split 玩到兩日嗎?  本來諗住去hvar 但係又好似差不多咁</blockquote><br />\n藍洞出海一日遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇台灣人去藍洞屌哂鬼  坐個幾鐘大飛睇十分鐘  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲要勁早出發, 分分鍾半邊身未訓醒 (好似 9am 左右就會係 hvar 出發, 即係要搭6am 班船去 Hvar <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)</blockquote><br />\n我之前search過split 都有團出  唔駛特登去hvar 上  同埋佢係會上島俾時間你遊城  都會玩成日   所以我都諗過下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來 Split 都有團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"944cfd51f200ce9894fee20ceafc81c3c5b00091","tid":266895,"uid":94033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:57:37.000Z","msg":"在 Split 有個相當有趣的博物館, 它叫 froggyland,專門展出青蛙標本。這些不是一般標本,負責製作的藝術家用青蛙標本製成一個個人類日常生活的場景,例如上課,運動會等, 真是大開眼界。<br />\n這些模型亦突顯了藝術家對細節的執著,模型內每隻青蛙的動作都稍有不同,絕不是倒模式製作,而且其他的道具造工亦相當精細,更讓人驚訝的是,原來這些青蛙標本已經有100年歷史。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2016/07/27/09/36A0F8E300000578-3710282-image-m-47_1469607608974.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2016%2F07%2F27%2F09%2F36A0F8E300000578-3710282-image-m-47_1469607608974.jpg&h=a04dbdba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>(因館內不得拍攝, 以網絡圖片代替 source: <a href=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/travel/travel_news/article-3710282/Hop-Inside-bizarre-taxidermy-museum-500-stuffed-frogs-seen-playing-tennis-going-school-performing-circus-acts.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Ftravel%2Ftravel_news%2Farticle-3710282%2FHop-Inside-bizarre-taxidermy-museum-500-stuffed-frogs-seen-playing-tennis-going-school-performing-circus-acts.html&d=Lz%2FlKVMzjY173D09amOymb5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=befe25c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.dailymail.co.uk/travel/travel_news/article-3710282/Hop-Inside-bizarre-taxidermy-museum-500-stuffed-frogs-seen-playing-tennis-going-school-performing-circus-acts.html</a>)</em>"}]}